-------------------------
ENIGMA IN THE WINE CELLAR
-------------------------

This is an exploration puzzle game played from a first-person point of view.
Explore rooms and passages to find hidden items.  The original version
of this game ran on the Palm OS platform.  This version for Linux OS
is an older OpenGL-based complete version 5.0 with modifications to bring
the rendering system more up-to-date (OpenGL 3.1).

AUTOTOOLS BUILD PACKAGE

The shell command './configure && make' should configure the build system
and then build this package.  No installation is done.  The resulting binary
file must be run within the src directory using the shell commands:

cd src
./enigma-in-the-wine-cellar
